                         n="25" break="no"/>māN gopāla-devaḥ kuśalī<g type="ddandaStrokeLeft">.</g> śrī-puṇḍravarddhana-bhuktau<g type="danda">.</g> caṇḍagrāma-viṣaya-samvaddha-suvarṇṇakārikā-daṇḍāt· <num value="4000">catuḥ<lb 
