                 </p>
                 <p>
                     viditam astu bhava<lb 
                         n="36" break="no"/>tān<unclear>·</unclear> yathopari-likhitāṅśeya sva-sīmā-paryantaḥ sa-talaḥ soddeśaḥ sa-pādapaḥ sa-jala-sthalaḥ sa-gartto<choice><orig>s</orig><corr>ṣ</corr></choice>araḥ sopa<lb 
