                     <l n="b">-kriyā-nataḥ <surplus>śrī-</surplus>śāntikaro vabhūva<g type="danda">.</g></l>
                     <l n="c">śrī-śūrapā<lb n="50" break="no"/>lasya narādhirāja</l>
